OL,3,CWatch: Striking images show thousands
OL,4,Cgather for mass Eid prayers
OL,6,FStriking images show thousands of
OL,7,Fpeople gathering to pray together to
OL,8,Fcelebrate the Islamic festival of Eid.
OL,10,FPrayers started at 9am in Small Heath
OL,11,FPark in Birmingham.
OL,13,FEvents are continuing until 9 pm, and
OL,14,Fa number of schools across Birmingham
OL,15,Fhave closed to allow their pupils to
OL,16,Fcelebrate the festival.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
