OL,3,CWatch: Striking images show thousands
OL,4,Cgather for mass Eid prayers
OL,6,FOne woman who attended told ITV
OL,7,FCentral the meaning of Eid for her:
OL,8,F"In all honesty the main message, and
OL,9,Fthe reason that you're going to get
OL,10,Fpeople in their absolute thousands
OL,11,Fhere, and every muslim on the planet
OL,12,Fpraying the Eid prayer, is because
OL,13,Fit's all about worshipping God, and
OL,14,Fgiving thanks to God.
OL,16,F"This prayer, even though it was so
OL,17,Fshort, really puts your focus back
OL,18,Fonto God and appreciating everything
OL,19,Fthat we've been given."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
