OL,3,CWatch: Striking images show thousands
OL,4,Cgather for mass Eid prayers
OL,6,FVictoria Park in Leicester also saw a
OL,7,Fthousands-strong crowd gather for
OL,8,Fprayers and food.
OL,10,FToday is the start of the three day
OL,11,Ffestival involving prayers, sporting
OL,12,Factivities and fun fair rides.
OL,14,FThe event in Leicester runs until 7pm
OL,15,Fand is open to all communities in the
OL,16,Fcity.
